<paragraph blockId="2.[1004,1803,778,1347]" pageId="2" pageNumber="229">
This recendy described species was previously included in. 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="E. Geoffroy Saint-Hilaire" baseAuthorityYear="1813" box="[1407,1521,1096,1135]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Asellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="229" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tridens">tridens</taxonomicName>
, from which it is distinct both in molecular and morphological features. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
